text: Altmärkische Wische is a municipality in the district Stendal, in Saxony- Anhalt, Germany. It was created on 1 January 2010 and consists of the former municipalities of Falkenberg, Lichterfelde, Neukirchen and Wendemark. In 2023 it had a population of 831 people. == References == Category:2010 establishments in Germany Category:Municipalities in Saxony-Anhalt
